{"word":"θέσμιος","slug":"θέσμιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>θέσμιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θεσμός'><el>θεσμός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>according to law, lawful</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>θέσμια, τά</el>, as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>, <i>laws, customs, rites</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; also in sg., <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}